	src/arch/solaris/solaris_native.c, src/arch/waveout/waveout.c,
	src/arch/windows/windows_native.c: Started to refactor backends. The
	first step was to make _alBlitBuffer a normal function, not a function
	pointer. The reason for the latter was the SDL backend, which has been
	modified accordingly.

