	already adds newlines.

2005-12-27  Sven Panne  <sven.panne@aedion.de>

	* src/arch/alsa/alsa.c: Always use "_near" variants of
	snd_pcm_hw_params_set_period_size and snd_pcm_hw_params_set_rate, this
	should fix problems for some soundcards (thanks to Shawn Kirst for
	pointing this out). Removed some unused variables. Fixed two warnings.

