2005-12-21  Sven Panne  <sven.panne@aedion.de>

	* Makefile.am, configure.ac, src/Makefile.am, src/arch/bsd/bsd_dsp.c,
	src/arch/darwin/darwin_native.c, src/arch/interface/platform.h,
