	* configure.ac, src/arch/alsa/alsa.c: Cleaned up ALSA detection.

	* configure.ac: Moved debugging-related options together. Renamed
	--enable-stub-notify to --enable-debug-stub, the former seems to be a
	cut-n-paste error. Added explanations for debugging-related #defines.

