	removed unused/obsolete stuff

2005-11-03  Sven Panne  <sven.panne@aedion.de>

	* src/alc/alc_context.c: Minor aesthetical changes in alcGetIntegerv.

2005-11-02  Sven Panne  <sven.panne@aedion.de>

	* src/alc/alc_context.c, src/alc/alc_device.h: Fixed error handling for
	alcGetIntegerv, previously a device was needed even for querying
	ALC_MAJOR_VERSION and ALC_MINOR_VERSION, which was wrong.

2005-10-27  Prakash Punnoor <prakash@punnoor.de>

	* src/arch/alsa/alsa.c: merge Dino Puller's patch for being 
	able to use alsa with dmix

	* configure.ac: make CFLAGS overrideable by user

