	Changed audio conversion channlification to move burden of
	monoification to load time as opposed to run time.

	* openal/linux/src/al_fft.c
	FFT tweaks

	* openal/linux/src/al_filter.c
	Changed audio conversion channlification to move burden of
	monoification to load time as opposed to run time.

